  "Description": {
    "English": "A custom-made <span class=\"name name-technology\">launch control</span> system for high-performance starships. Sensitive gyroscopes and specialised control circuits plot custom take-off routines for increased launch <span class=\"name name-stellar\">speed</span> and <span class=\"name name-stellar\">efficiency</span>.<br> <br>Specialised, <span class=\"name name-technology\">deuterium-derived fuel</span> is required to recharge thruster. Launch procedures require sufficient fuel levels before activation.<br> <br>Hold <span class=\"name name-img\">THRUST</span> to take off from planet. Hold <span class=\"name name-img\">BOOST</span> to initiate in-flight speed boost.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "为高性能飞船准备的定制化<span class=\"name name-technology\">发射操控</span>系统。高敏度陀螺仪，特殊化的控制电路外加特别定制的起飞流程将能够大幅提高发射<span class=\"name name-stellar\">速度</span>以及<span class=\"name name-stellar\">效率</span>。<br><br>专门提炼的<span class=\"name name-technology\">氘基燃料</span>将为推进器提供能量。只有为飞船提供了充足的燃料之后，才能启动发射程序。<br><br>长按<span class=\"name name-img\">THRUST</span>离开行星地表。在飞行时长按<span class=\"name name-img\">BOOST</span>启动加速。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "高效能太空船適用的自訂<span class=\"name name-technology\">發射控制</span>系統。裝備可大幅提升發射<span class=\"name name-stellar\">速度</span>和<span class=\"name name-stellar\">效率</span>的敏感陀螺儀與專用控制電路圖客製化起飛程序。<br> <br>需使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">氘製專屬燃料</span>補充推進器能源。需有充足燃料才能夠啟動發射程序。<br> <br>按住<span class=\"name name-img\">THRUST</span>從星球起飛。按住<span class=\"name name-img\">BOOST</span>啟動飛行加速功能。"
  },
